              <p>For further information on cookies generally visit <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org">www.aboutcookies.org</a> or <a href="https://www.allaboutcookies.org">www.allaboutcookies.org</a></p>
              <h2>3. Types of cookies:</h2>
              <p>The cookies we place on your device fall into the following categories:</p>
